br />\n我理解係：支那就係中共國。一個支那人，就係大陸公民。文化嘅嘢涉及民族，而支那人從來都唔係中華人民共和國國內任何一個民族嘅稱呼，而係國民嘅稱呼。所以同中國菜無關、同着華服無關、同語言、文字都無關。<br />\n混淆民族同國民，有機會係中共統戰嘅手法，機智嘅連登仔點會中計呢？"},{"pid":"045d2831abb6b6f9e55fb45d3e26a9d56d6ceada","tid":760363,"uid":63779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa4ccf1a9fef1bd868f1e9f8fe41c491f63f1e00","tid":760363,"uid":146621,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T13:50:10.000Z","msg":"黨國不分黎講<br />\n無論正反面都算洗腦成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T18:45:28.000Z","msg":"自新移民到自由行到單非雙非父母，仲有得分黨國咩?"},{"pid":"4bff792b41370ed25b3ed6a54a4a64b5c40924ba","tid":760363,"uid":112935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa5a12ce5f45c99e185712e5c0e85a41aa561180","tid":760363,"uid":108467,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T12:50:15.000Z","msg":"你喺香港食有乜問題，你返去大陸食元素過期表就on9姐。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T19:00:03.000Z","msg":"岩聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4610923f22fa4e70a6ca906da2716655073d8f33","tid":760363,"uid":109050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25482f8e64282bac894193161b03ab068b13fb7b","tid":760363,"uid":46245,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T13:04:52.000Z","msg":"唔會，唔通你食m記就被視為美國人咩，你諗多左啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T19:01:37.000Z","msg":"咁點解用大陸機就話人蝗既"},{"pid":"0f26831fe477c801da1699559c109fb8f1f31573","tid":760363,"uid":159916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T19:08:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05fea7bd2c6a4ed4dd2bd93befb593cf9f02c037","tid":760363,"uid":147226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T22:52:01.000Z","msg":"講真，好多南方野/粵菜支那已經食唔到，反而香港仲保留住<br />\n<br />\n反而啲北方野完全唔明點解會流行<br />\n咩野都整到辣一辣，人地北方就用來禦寒，香港啲食肆就用來蓋過啲肉啲腐爛味，港豬就衝去食辣野出晒汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi